transcript:
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Haan good morning sir. Kahan se bol rahe ho?
Executive: Main phone kar raha hun aapko aap itna phone kyun kar rahe ho? Main busy hai main phone kar raha hun aapko.
summary:
\n
Concerns:\n
- Customer asked where the executive was calling from.\n
- Customer asked why the executive was calling.\n
\n
Resolution:\n
- Executive stated he was calling the customer and questioned why the customer was calling so much.\n
- Executive mentioned he was busy.\n
\n
Next Steps: \n
Issue not resolved.\n
\n
Alert (If Any):\n
None\n

Neutral to annoyed.\n
\n

call origin, call purpose, busy
